      <tr><td colspan=1  style='font-size: 9.5px;'>37 threads, <a href=item.html?item=3990&start=0>1</a> <a href=item.html?item=3990&start=25>2</a>  page(s) long</td><td  style='font-size: 9.5px;' align=right>&nbsp;<a href=item.html?item=3990&start=25>Next Page</a></td></tr></table></form><ul><table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=10353945391214></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f10353945391214><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=item.html?item=3990&mid=10353945391214>Solo</a> <a id=fs8 href=item.html?item=3990&mid=10353945391214#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=176823><span id= >seekers</span></a>, <span id= > </span><br><span id=notbold>1 posts</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Wed, Oct 23rd 1:54 PM 2002</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[3.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>OK this is what happened to me. did a pop in to see if gleed was up. Now remember this is one day after POP when live and I have never been in this zone before. (Ranger by the way). Camo up, Sow, and I run around checking out the place. I do a who to see who can give me a hand. I am the only one in the zone. So I walk around to get the lay of the land. I have a idea as to where he is and I am careful because I know he has 3 see inv giants around him. At this point I am lost. (Thanks VI for the great maps) turn around and get the smack down layed upon me. Inv drops, ok don't worry still got sow so I run around alittle. Now I am getting hit with spells and I know what is comming next so I do a /loc. Next thing I see is Loading please wait....<br><br>Go back and get my body and lucky me there are some lvl 60's in the zone. I find my body and send them a tell asking if they can pull the see inv guards so I can do the turn-in for my bow. They in turn ask if I am a ranger and if the king is up. I do a track and he is. I let her know and she said ok once her friends come she will try to help me out. 5 min go by and I am still checking out the place when I do a who in the zone. 75 lvl 63 people in zone. I get a /ooc Please help seeker get his turn in for he is the one who spotted that the king was up. Next think I know the two guards are dead and it is open for me.<br><br>Now the fun Part..<br>I sneak in Inv up hugging the left wall as was posted here. find the pole with the flag and get as close as possiable, duck as was posted. Guess what went wrong.... Yep I forgot to drop Inv.... It gets better. I am thinking that I am still not close enough so I look at my feet to move closer and I drop off the cliff.... I got lucky, no argo yet so I drop my inv behind gleed and do the turn in. I am very happy and all the lvl 63 peeps are giving me grats. So all I have to do is inv up and sneak out of dodge. WRONG.&nbsp;&nbsp;The spell drops my sneak so I start running.. Made the first step, made the second, did not make the third... err.Loading please wait....I start my run from Thurg back. Now I am like who cares I got my bow I can make up the xp loss. Zone into EW inv and sowed with all my 3 ac buffs on. And low and behold I get jumped by some death group.. Try to make it to the zone at KD and there is a small problem, it seems that so many of the peeps in the guild that was killing the king zoned in that the zone crashed... /OOC Naked ranger with death squd in tow stay away... Finnaly the zone comes on line and I zone in. Seems the king despawned from the crash.. everyone is now in the arena for drops or faction (this is the number 1 guild on legends - L-12)and here I am naked no weapons, money and no way to get my stuff back. I get a /ooc anyone know where gleed is I need to do a turn in. Seems there is a lvl 51 ranger who needs some help. I send him a tell we hhok up and the see inv are up again. So I consent him and try to pull the inv mobs so he can do the turn in and grab my corpse. I hit one guard with snare and make a run for the wl zone. with one bulb I send him a tell that I made it.. Seems only one of the guards came eeeeerrrrrrr. So I heal up and try again.. Check track and guess what gleed is not even up... Bottom line I made some good friends with the ranger, a necro who tryed to charge me 100pp to summon my corpse (he did it for free) I owe him one, and I got my bow.<br><br>For all of the people out there who are not in a guild and always solo... Good Luck<br><br>Seekerx<br>Lvl 46 ranger<br>Legends<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
